<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>7</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ni tabibu wa karibu;
 Tabibu wa ajabu;
 Na rehema za daima;
 Ni dawa yake njema.

[V2]
 Imbeni, malaika,
 Sifa za Yesu Bwana;
 Pweke limetukuka
 Jina lake Yesu.

[V3]
 Hatufai kuwa hai,
 Wala hatutumai,
 Ila kweli yeye ndiye
 Atupumzishaye.

[V4]
 Dhambi pia na hatia
 Ametuchukulia;
 Twendeni na amani
 Hata kwake Mbinguni.

[V5]
 Huliona tamu jina
 La Yesu Kristo Bwana,
 Yuna sifa mwenye kufa
 Asishindwe na kufa.

[V6]
 Kila mume asimame,
 Sifa zake zivume;
 Wanawake na washike
 Kusifu jina lake.

[V7]
 Na vijana wote tena,
 Wampendao sana
 Waje kwake wawe wake
 Kwa utumishi wake.</lyrics>
<title>Ni tabibu wa Karibu TZR7</title>
</song>